<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>SOS Venezuela — Información y coordinación de ayuda | Fundación Eugenio Mendoza</title>
<meta name="description" content="Página informativa de la Fundación Eugenio Mendoza sobre la respuesta humanitaria al terremoto de Venezuela (La Guaira, junio 2026): organismos de ayuda, plataformas de información y protocolo de priorización.">
<meta property="og:title" content="SOS Venezuela — Información de ayuda humanitaria | Fundación Eugenio Mendoza">
<meta property="og:description" content="Directorio informativo de organismos de ayuda, plataformas de búsqueda de personas y protocolo de priorización ante el terremoto de Venezuela 2026.">
<meta property="og:type" content="website">
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js@4.4.1/dist/chart.umd.min.js"></script>
<style>
  :root{
    --ve-yellow:#FCDD09; --ve-blue:#00247D; --ve-blue2:#0033A0; --ve-red:#CF142B;
    --ink:#16202e; --ink-soft:#475467; --line:#e4e7ec; --bg:#f7f8fa; --card:#ffffff;
    --shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(16,24,40,.06),0 8px 24px rgba(16,24,40,.06);
    --shadow-lg:0 12px 40px rgba(16,24,40,.16);
    --radius:16px; --maxw:1160px;
    --p1:#0033A0; --p2:#1d72c2; --p3:#7aa7d8;
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box}
  html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
  body{margin:0;font-family:'Segoe UI',system-ui,-apple-system,Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color:var(--ink);background:var(--bg);line-height:1.55;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}
  a{color:var(--ve-blue2)}
  .wrap{max-width:var(--maxw);margin:0 auto;padding:0 22px}
  h1,h2,h3{line-height:1.2;margin:0}
  .muted{color:var(--ink-soft)}

  /* NAV */
  header.nav{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:50;background:rgba(255,255,255,.92);backdrop-filter:blur(10px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}
  .nav-in{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;height:64px}
  .nav-logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:11px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.3px;text-decoration:none;color:var(--ink)}
  .femlogo{display:inline-flex;align-items:center}
  .femlogo img,.femlogo svg{display:block;width:auto}
  .femlogo.nav{background:#fff;padding:5px 9px;border-radius:7px}
  .femlogo.nav img,.femlogo.nav svg{height:30px}
  .nav-logo .flag{width:34px;height:23px;border-radius:4px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);flex:none}
  .nav-links{margin-left:auto;display:flex;gap:6px;flex-wrap:wrap}
  .nav-links a{padding:9px 14px;border-radius:10px;text-decoration:none;color:var(--ink-soft);font-weight:600;font-size:14.5px}
  .nav-links a:hover{background:var(--bg);color:var(--ink)}
  .nav-toggle{display:none;margin-left:auto;background:none;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:10px;padding:8px 11px;font-size:18px;cursor:pointer}

  /* HERO */
  .hero{position:relative;color:#fff;overflow:hidden;background:#0a1a3a}
  .hero-img{position:absolute;inset:0;background-size:cover;background-position:center;filter:saturate(1.02)}
  .hero-img::after{content:"";position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(7,17,40,.55) 0%,rgba(7,17,40,.72) 45%,rgba(7,17,40,.92) 100%)}
  .hero-in{position:relative;z-index:2;padding:74px 0 56px}
  .hero-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.22);padding:7px 14px;border-radius:999px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.4px}
  .hero-badge .dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--ve-red);box-shadow:0 0 0 4px rgba(207,20,43,.3);animation:pulse 1.8s infinite}
  @keyframes pulse{0%{box-shadow:0 0 0 0 rgba(207,20,43,.5)}70%{box-shadow:0 0 0 9px rgba(207,20,43,0)}100%{box-shadow:0 0 0 0 rgba(207,20,43,0)}}
  .hero h1{font-size:clamp(44px,8vw,92px);font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-1.5px;margin:20px 0 6px;text-shadow:0 2px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.4)}
  .hero h1 .flagbar{display:inline-block;width:auto}
  .hero-sub{font-size:clamp(17px,2.4vw,22px);max-width:720px;color:#e9eef7;font-weight:500}
  .hero-flag{display:inline-flex;vertical-align:middle;width:62px;height:42px;border-radius:6px;box-shadow:0 4px 14px rgba(0,0,0,.35);margin-left:6px}
  .hero-cta{margin-top:30px;display:flex;gap:13px;flex-wrap:wrap}
  .btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;padding:13px 22px;border-radius:12px;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;font-size:15px;border:1px solid transparent;cursor:pointer;transition:transform .12s ease, box-shadow .12s}
  .btn:active{transform:translateY(1px)}
  .btn-primary{background:var(--ve-yellow);color:#3a2e00}
  .btn-primary:hover{box-shadow:0 8px 22px rgba(252,221,9,.35)}
  .btn-ghost{background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);color:#fff;border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.3)}
  .btn-ghost:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.18)}
  .hero-credit{position:absolute;right:12px;bottom:8px;z-index:2;font-size:10.5px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.6)}
  .hero-logo{position:absolute;top:20px;right:22px;z-index:4;background:#fff;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.10);border-radius:13px;padding:11px 16px;box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.30)}
  .hero-logo .femlogo img,.hero-logo .femlogo svg{height:46px}
  @media(max-width:640px){.hero-logo{top:12px;right:12px;padding:7px 11px}.hero-logo img{height:30px}}

  /* DISCLAIMER */
  .disclaimer{background:#fff8e6;border-top:3px solid var(--ve-yellow);border-bottom:1px solid #f1e4b8}
  .disclaimer-in{display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:flex-start;padding:18px 0}
  .disclaimer .ico{font-size:24px;flex:none;line-height:1}
  .disclaimer p{margin:0;font-size:14.5px;color:#6b5a16}
  .disclaimer strong{color:#4a3f0e}

  /* STATS */
  section{padding:62px 0}
  .sec-head{max-width:760px;margin-bottom:34px}
  .eyebrow{display:inline-block;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ve-blue2);margin-bottom:10px}
  .sec-head h2{font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,40px);font-weight:850;letter-spacing:-.5px}
  .sec-head p{margin-top:12px;font-size:16.5px;color:var(--ink-soft)}

  .stats{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:18px}
  .stat{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:24px 22px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);position:relative;overflow:hidden}
  .stat::before{content:"";position:absolute;left:0;top:0;bottom:0;width:5px;background:var(--ve-blue2)}
  .stat.r::before{background:var(--ve-red)} .stat.y::before{background:var(--ve-yellow)} .stat.g::before{background:#1d72c2}
  .stat .num{font-size:38px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-1px;line-height:1}
  .stat .lbl{margin-top:8px;font-size:13.5px;color:var(--ink-soft);font-weight:600}
  .stat .sublbl{font-size:11.5px;color:#98a2b3;margin-top:3px}

  .charts{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.1fr 1.1fr 1fr;gap:18px;margin-top:22px}
  .chart-card{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:20px;box-shadow:var(--shadow)}
  .chart-card h3{font-size:15px;font-weight:750;margin-bottom:4px}
  .chart-card .ch-sub{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--ink-soft);margin-bottom:14px}
  .chart-box{position:relative;height:210px}

  /* TABS / FILTERS */
  .filters{display:flex;gap:9px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:26px}
  .chip{padding:9px 16px;border-radius:999px;border:1px solid var(--line);background:#fff;color:var(--ink-soft);font-weight:650;font-size:14px;cursor:pointer;transition:.15s}
  .chip:hover{border-color:#c3cad6}
  .chip.active{background:var(--ve-blue2);color:#fff;border-color:var(--ve-blue2);box-shadow:0 6px 16px rgba(0,51,160,.22)}
  .chip .cnt{opacity:.65;font-weight:700;margin-left:5px}

  /* CARD GRID */
  .grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:18px}
  .card{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:22px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);cursor:pointer;transition:transform .14s ease, box-shadow .14s, border-color .14s;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;position:relative}
  .card:hover{transform:translateY(-4px);box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg);border-color:#cdd6e4}
  .card .tag-row{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center}
  .pill{font-size:11px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.4px;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:999px;text-transform:uppercase}
  .pill.p1{background:#e7eeff;color:#0033A0} .pill.p2{background:#e7f2fb;color:#1668a8} .pill.p3{background:#eef3f9;color:#5b7da6}
  .pill.type{background:#f2eefb;color:#6b3fb0}
  .pill.order{background:var(--ve-blue2);color:#fff}
  .pill.warn{background:#fdeceb;color:#b42318} .pill.ok{background:#e9f6ec;color:#177a3a} .pill.mid{background:#fff4e2;color:#b25e00}
  .card h3{font-size:17.5px;font-weight:780;letter-spacing:-.2px}
  .card .meta{font-size:13px;color:var(--ink-soft);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
  .card .excerpt{font-size:13.8px;color:var(--ink-soft);display:-webkit-box;-webkit-line-clamp:3;-webkit-box-orient:vertical;overflow:hidden}
  .card .open{margin-top:auto;font-size:13px;font-weight:750;color:var(--ve-blue2);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
  .card.proto{cursor:pointer}
  .card .ordernum{position:absolute;top:18px;right:20px;font-size:40px;font-weight:900;color:#eef1f6;line-height:1}

  /* recaudo de insumos */
  .orglogos{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:16px;margin-bottom:34px}
  .logo-card{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--radius);box-shadow:var(--shadow);height:120px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:22px}
  .logo-card img{max-width:100%;max-height:100%;object-fit:contain}
  .recaudo-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:30px;align-items:start}
  .insumos{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:10px}
  .insumo{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:11px;padding:12px 14px;font-size:13.8px;box-shadow:var(--shadow)}
  .insumo .ic{color:var(--ve-blue2);flex:none;font-size:16px;line-height:1.3}
  .acopio{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px}
  .acopio-city{font-size:12.5px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ve-red);margin:6px 0 2px}
  .acopio .card{cursor:default}
  .acopio .card:hover{transform:none;box-shadow:var(--shadow);border-color:var(--line)}
  .acopio h3{font-size:15.5px}
  .acopio .addr{font-size:13.3px;color:var(--ink-soft)}
  .acopio .hr{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--ve-blue2);font-weight:650;margin-top:4px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
  @media(max-width:760px){.orglogos{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}.recaudo-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.insumos{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}}
  @media(max-width:480px){.insumos{grid-template-columns:1fr}}

  /* sub-step for platforms */
  .substep{display:none}
  .substep.show{display:block;animation:fade .3s ease}
  @keyframes fade{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px)}to{opacity:1;transform:none}}
  .back-link{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ve-blue2);background:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:14.5px;margin-bottom:18px;padding:0}

  /* MODAL */
  .modal-bg{position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(12,20,40,.55);backdrop-filter:blur(3px);z-index:100;display:none;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:center;padding:40px 18px;overflow-y:auto}
  .modal-bg.show{display:flex}
  .modal{background:#fff;border-radius:20px;max-width:680px;width:100%;box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg);animation:pop .22s ease;overflow:hidden}
  @keyframes pop{from{opacity:0;transform:scale(.96) translateY(10px)}to{opacity:1;transform:none}}
  .modal-head{padding:26px 28px 20px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);position:relative;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#fbfcfe,#fff)}
  .modal-head .tag-row{margin-bottom:12px}
  .modal-head h2{font-size:24px;font-weight:850;letter-spacing:-.4px;padding-right:36px}
  .modal-close{position:absolute;top:20px;right:20px;width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:50%;border:1px solid var(--line);background:#fff;cursor:pointer;font-size:17px;color:var(--ink-soft);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
  .modal-close:hover{background:var(--bg)}
  .modal-body{padding:8px 28px 30px;max-height:none}
  .field{padding:16px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #f0f2f5}
  .field:last-child{border-bottom:none}
  .field .k{font-size:11.5px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ve-blue2);margin-bottom:6px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px}
  .field .v{font-size:14.8px;color:var(--ink)}
  .field .v.fem{background:#fff8e6;border:1px solid #f1e4b8;border-radius:10px;padding:12px 14px;color:#5b4d12}
  .links a{display:block;font-size:13.5px;margin:4px 0;word-break:break-all}
  .contact-line{display:block;margin:3px 0;font-size:14px}

  /* FOOTER */
  footer{background:#0c1830;color:#c7d2e4;padding:50px 0 30px;margin-top:20px}
  footer .f-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.4fr 1fr 1fr;gap:34px}
  footer h4{color:#fff;font-size:15px;margin-bottom:14px}
  footer a{color:#9fb3d4;text-decoration:none;display:block;margin:7px 0;font-size:14px}
  footer a:hover{color:#fff}
  footer .f-logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:14px}
  footer .f-logo .femlogo.foot{background:#243140;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);padding:11px 15px;border-radius:11px;box-shadow:0 6px 18px rgba(0,0,0,.30)}
  footer .f-logo .femlogo.foot img,footer .f-logo .femlogo.foot svg{height:50px}
  .f-disc{font-size:13px;color:#8093b2;max-width:420px}
  .f-bottom{border-top:1px solid #21314f;margin-top:34px;padding-top:20px;font-size:12.5px;color:#7184a6;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px}
  .emerg{background:#3a0d12;border:1px solid #5e1620;border-radius:12px;padding:14px 16px;margin-top:10px}
  .emerg b{color:#ffb4bd}

  @media(max-width:900px){
    .stats{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}
    .charts{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
    footer .f-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
  }
  @media(max-width:640px){
    .nav-links{display:none;position:absolute;top:64px;left:0;right:0;background:#fff;flex-direction:column;padding:10px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);box-shadow:var(--shadow)}
    .nav-links.open{display:flex}
    .nav-links a{padding:12px 10px}
    .nav-toggle{display:block}
    .grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .stats{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
    .hero-in{padding:54px 0 44px}
    footer .f-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .modal-body,.modal-head{padding-left:20px;padding-right:20px}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<header class="nav">
  <div class="wrap nav-in">
    <a class="nav-logo" href="#inicio">
      <span class="femlogo nav"><img src="https://fundacioneugeniomendoza.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/logo.png" alt="Fundación Eugenio Mendoza" onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'"></span>
      <svg class="flag" viewBox="0 0 60 40" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="60" height="40" fill="#00247D"/><rect width="60" height="13.33" fill="#FCDD09"/><rect y="26.66" width="60" height="13.34" fill="#CF142B"/><g fill="#fff"><circle cx="22" cy="22" r="1.3"/><circle cx="26" cy="21" r="1.3"/><circle cx="30" cy="20.6" r="1.3"/><circle cx="34" cy="21" r="1.3"/><circle cx="38" cy="22" r="1.3"/></g></svg>
      <span>SOS&nbsp;Venezuela</span>
    </a>
    <button class="nav-toggle" onclick="document.getElementById('navlinks').classList.toggle('open')">☰</button>
    <nav class="nav-links" id="navlinks">
      <a href="#panorama">Panorama</a>
      <a href="#organismos">Organismos de ayuda</a>
      <a href="#plataformas">Plataformas de información</a>
      <a href="#protocolo">Priorización y protocolo</a>
      <a href="#recaudo">Recaudo de insumos</a>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero" id="inicio" style="padding:0">
  <div class="hero-img" style="background-image:url('https://media.elestimulo.com/uploads/2026/06/image-1782386823.webp')"></div>
  <div class="hero-logo"><span class="femlogo hero"><img src="https://fundacioneugeniomendoza.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/logo.png" alt="Fundación Eugenio Mendoza" onerror="this.closest('.hero-logo').style.display='none'"></span></div>
  <div class="wrap hero-in">
    <span class="hero-badge"><span class="dot"></span> Terremoto de Venezuela · La Guaira · 24 de junio de 2026</span>
    <h1>SOS Venezuela
      <svg class="hero-flag" viewBox="0 0 60 40" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="60" height="40" fill="#00247D"/><rect width="60" height="13.33" fill="#FCDD09"/><rect y="26.66" width="60" height="13.34" fill="#CF142B"/><g fill="#fff"><circle cx="20" cy="22" r="1.4"/><circle cx="25" cy="20.8" r="1.4"/><circle cx="30" cy="20.4" r="1.4"/><circle cx="35" cy="20.8" r="1.4"/><circle cx="40" cy="22" r="1.4"/></g></svg>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Centro de información de la <strong>Fundación Eugenio Mendoza</strong> para orientar la ayuda humanitaria tras el terremoto: organismos confiables, plataformas de búsqueda de personas y un protocolo de priorización responsable.</p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#organismos">Ver organismos de ayuda</a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="#plataformas">Buscar personas / información</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <span class="hero-credit">Imagen referencial: edificio en Tanaguarena, La Guaira · cortesía El Estímulo</span>
</section>

<!-- DISCLAIMER -->
<div class="disclaimer" id="alcance">
  <div class="wrap disclaimer-in">
    <span class="ico">ℹ️</span>
    <p><strong>Alcance de esta página.</strong> Este sitio de la <strong>Fundación Eugenio Mendoza (FEM)</strong> tiene un carácter <strong>meramente informativo y de orientación</strong>. Reúne y enlaza fuentes públicas para facilitar la coordinación de ayuda; <strong>la FEM no gestiona donaciones a través de esta página, no recauda fondos aquí, no valida ni se hace responsable del contenido de terceros, y no almacena ni publica datos personales</strong> de personas desaparecidas, localizadas u hospitalizadas. Verifique siempre la información con los canales oficiales antes de difundirla o actuar. Ante peligro inmediato, contacte a los servicios de emergencia.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- PANORAMA / STATS + CHARTS -->
<section id="panorama">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">Panorama de la respuesta</span>
      <h2>Una emergencia que exige coordinación, no improvisación</h2>
      <p>Cifras de referencia del evento y de la red de respuesta sistematizada por la FEM. Los datos del impacto provienen de fuentes oficiales y de prensa y se actualizan constantemente; úselos como orientación, no como balance definitivo.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="stats">
      <div class="stat r"><div class="num">7,2 / 7,5</div><div class="lbl">Magnitud del doblete sísmico</div><div class="sublbl">24 jun 2026 · 18:04 hora local</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="num">+100</div><div class="lbl">Edificios colapsados en La Guaira</div><div class="sublbl">Estado más afectado</div></div>
      <div class="stat y"><div class="num">11</div><div class="lbl">Organismos de ayuda mapeados</div><div class="sublbl">Por la FEM, con uso recomendado</div></div>
      <div class="stat g"><div class="num">8</div><div class="lbl">Plataformas de información</div><div class="sublbl">Búsqueda y localización de personas</div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="charts">
      <div class="chart-card">
        <h3>Organismos por rubro de ayuda</h3>
        <div class="ch-sub">Cuántas organizaciones cubren cada rubro</div>
        <div class="chart-box"><canvas id="chPrioridad"></canvas></div>
      </div>
      <div class="chart-card">
        <h3>Ámbito de acción de los organismos</h3>
        <div class="ch-sub">Dónde opera principalmente cada aliado</div>
        <div class="chart-box"><canvas id="chAmbito"></canvas></div>
      </div>
      <div class="chart-card">
        <h3>Verificación de las plataformas</h3>
        <div class="ch-sub">La mayoría son ciudadanas y sin verificar: precaución</div>
        <div class="chart-box"><canvas id="chVerif"></canvas></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ORGANISMOS -->
<section id="organismos" style="background:#fff;border-top:1px solid var(--line);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)">
  <div class="wrap">
